# Zod Schemas

## `src/schemas/telegram-schema.ts`

Validate and extract only needed fields from Telegram updates:

* `update_id`
* `message.chat.id`
* `message.from.id`
* `message.message_id`
* `message.date`
* `message.text`

Ignore in step 2:

* photos/files
* callback queries
* edited messages
* group admin events

Only process plain text `message.text` updates.

