# Security

## Hard rules for Step 2

1. exactly one allowed chat id
2. optional exact allowed user id
3. no replies to unknown chats/users
4. no auto-trusting new users
5. bot token only from local config/env

## Out of scope (future steps)

* multi-user support
* group chat support
* role-based controls
* dynamic onboarding via agent conversation
* command ACL matrix

